catalogEntries.title: BP Gift Token
catalogEntries.description:
Give a friend the Chapter 4 Season 2 Battle Pass! Your purchase includes:

- A token allowing gifting of the Chapter 4 Season 2 Battle Pass to a friend of your choice.
- A unique Gift Box for you to use when gifting items from the Battle Royale shop (unlocks only once).

Note: In order to gift, you must have multi-factor authentication enabled on your account. You must also be Epic friends with the recipient for at least 48 hours before you can send them a gift.

You will only be able to gift five times within a 24 hour period. Any gifts that are purchased or received are NOT refundable. You can only gift one Battle Pass at a time.

If your intended recipient purchases the Battle Pass or subscribes to the Fortnite Crew before you complete your purchase, you can gift the Battle Pass to someone else. If you dont gift the Battle Pass by the end of the season, it will be refunded as 950 V-Bucks in your account.

catalogEntries.title: Metal Team Leader Pack
catalogEntries.description: Cold steel, warm heart!

catalogEntries.title: Crossmark Operative Pack
catalogEntries.description: Being a self-taught expert in stealth and style means you get to blend in but still stand out. Carry out your next mission with the Crossmark Operative Pack.

catalogEntries.title: Fully Realized Pack
catalogEntries.description: With her Teth-R 128 VR/AR System, Colby is always ready to play. Roll along with her using the Fully Realized Pack. Includes access to "Save the World" PvE Campaign.

catalogEntries.title: Skate Park Royalty Pack
catalogEntries.description: With their chill confidence and effortless style, Toni rules the ramps.

catalogEntries.title: Robo-Ray
catalogEntries.description: Everything's fine, she has a plan, and she's gonna fix this!

catalogEntries.title: Mecha-Pop Pack
catalogEntries.description: Our trusted storm shield mechanic and crackling companion: Mecha-Pop.

catalogEntries.title: Robo-Kevin Pack
catalogEntries.description: Everyone's favorite triangular bot is here to upgrade your spirits.

catalogEntries.title: Lok-Bot
catalogEntries.description: Imagine, if you will, an oven bot and the places he will go.

catalogEntries.title: Samurai Scrapper Pack
catalogEntries.description: One person's trash is another person's armor!
